 * RF24Ethernet Arduino library by TMRh20 - 2014-2015
 *
 * Automated (mesh) wireless networking and TCP/IP communication stack for RF24 radio modules
 *
 * RF24 -> RF24Network -> UIP(TCP/IP) -> RF24Ethernet
